Clawd sprite assets in this directory (sprite_*.h) are vendored from:

    clawd-tank
    https://github.com/marciogranzotto/clawd-tank
    Copyright (c) 2026 Marcio Granzotto Rodrigues
    Licensed under the MIT License.

The sprites are RLE-compressed RGB565 frames (auto-generated by the upstream
project's tools/png2rgb565.py) depicting "Clawd", the Claude Code mascot.

Only the firmware sprite data headers are vendored. The decode + render logic
in src/buddy_clawd.{h,cpp} is original to this project.

